---
title: Mediterranean Tomato & Cannellini Bean Soup with Kale & Cheesy Garlic Ciabatta
description: Settle in for a cosy night with this hearty cannellini bean and tomato soup. Full of colourful veggies and classic
Mediterranean flavours, the meal gets an extra boost with addictive cheesy ciabatta toasts on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mediterranean-tomato-cannellini-bean-soup-0ea5dbce.jpg
